    <title>Inference Based on Time-Varying SVARs Identified with Sign Restrictions</title>
    <updated>2026-01-23T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Jonas E Arias, Juan F Rubio Ramírez, Minchul Shin, Daniel F Waggoner</name>
