    <title>Delegation and Chief Financial Officer Retention: Evidence from Chief Accounting Officers on the Executive Team</title>
    <updated>2026-01-27T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Leah Muriel, Adrienne Rhodes, Dan Russomanno</name>
